name: Number Station Hoax
description:
I've always been obsessed with radiowaves and tapes. Here's my latest creation – a simulation of a numberstation (or spy radio station) that I crafted using AI-generated music and text-to-speech software. 

Processed with Tascam tape portastudio 424 + Fuji JP II-90 Type II cassette.

The footage is an analog 2018 film shot of Budapest made with an East German Praktica Super TL2 camera + Astrum b/w film.
